        "content": "<p>Consider the following example:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">foo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">String</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Bool</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Id</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">run</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ValidPos</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">startValidPos</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">while</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≠</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">endValidPos</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">-- `h` works here</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">true</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">then</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">-- comment out to fix</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">pure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">()</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">-- `h` refers to inaccessible `i`, not the one in context, ergo error</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">true</span>\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">print</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">foo</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>On <code>#print</code>ing <code>foo</code>, it's clear what's happening:</p>\n<div class=\"spoiler-block\"><div class=\"spoiler-header\">\n<p>#print foo</p>\n</div><div class=\"spoiler-content\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">foo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">String</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Bool</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">startValidPos</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">forIn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Loop</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mk</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">          </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">          </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≠</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">endValidPos</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">then</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">__</span><span class=\"n\">do_jp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">              </span><span class=\"n\">pure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">()</span>\n<span class=\"w\">              </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ValidPos</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⋯</span>\n<span class=\"w\">              </span><span class=\"n\">pure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PUnit</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">unit</span>\n<span class=\"w\">              </span><span class=\"n\">pure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ForInStep</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">yield</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">true</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">true</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">then</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">              </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">()</span>\n<span class=\"w\">              </span><span class=\"bp\">__</span><span class=\"n\">do_jp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">              </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">()</span>\n<span class=\"w\">              </span><span class=\"bp\">__</span><span class=\"n\">do_jp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"w\">          </span><span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ForInStep</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">done</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ValidPos</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">r</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">pure</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">true</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">run</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</div></div>\n<p>We do not revert the forward dependencies of <code>i</code> when abstracting <code>i</code> in <code>have __do_jp := fun i y =&gt; do ...</code>, so <code>h</code> is no longer about the <code>i</code> inside the <code>fun</code>. We could, however, give <code>__do_jp</code> a signature of <code>(i : s.ValidPos) -&gt; (h : i ≠ s.endValidPos) -&gt; Unit -&gt; _</code>, pass along <code>h</code>, and everything would work out.</p>\n<p>Are forward dependencies just too costly to compute here, or could this be fixed? (Or is there some other reason fixing this is a bad idea?)</p>",
